Hi Sunny,

One problem with a batch of jobs is that there is no guarantee that the jobs will finish within the 
reasonable time window. If you don&#39;t have resource to &#39;babysit&#39; these jobs so that you can make 
decision on fly you should probably set some global limits such as:

- max-time-sec -- maximum time duration of a crawl

- max-bytes-download -- maximum bytes to download per crawl

- max-document-download -- maximum documents to download per crawl

If you set some of these limits be aware that hitting crawler traps or &#39;junk&#39; pages may directly 
effect the quality of your crawls.

Take care
i.

